trans-unit.target: TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_000<tab>The power was mine... I obtained the unmeasurable, and now my end is come.
TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_002<tab>Not an end, you say? We continue onwards...together?
TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_004<tab>Your contribution to my experiment is appreciated. Without your unrelenting strength, I would never have realized this new potential.
TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_005<tab>I will embark on a journey, observing and recording all that I encounter. Farewell, mortals. This world has much to teach me...
